Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strongest Duelists from all over the world clash during the World Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One must collect five Heart Pieces in order to enter the Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already got four Heart Pieces! I'm definitely making it to the Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dear brave Duelists, you've endured the Duel Carnival until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow is your last day to compete for Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warriors, rest up for now \Nand prepare to assault once again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you use Photon Mode to Number Hunt far too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep it up, Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}, your body will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep your mouth shut and continue gathering information on the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm steadily collecting the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cure your sickness very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just endure it a bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, I went so far to root for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the least you can do to thank me for not abandoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... You're gonna get fat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,507)}"Number 40:\N The Visitor from Heartland, Haruto"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(624,514)}He most likely activated some kind of power during the moment of the crash,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(613,518)}which sent everything within that dimension flying back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(672,518)}Just what is this young boy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could you be able to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even talk to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear this child out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Guess there's no helping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! That was my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man oh man, he went and put a giant hole in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he was in a surprisingly bold mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so carefree about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Heartland hears about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we shouldn't let Kaito hear about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mood'll be scary if he hears Haruto went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This evening in C Block of the eastern area of the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at intersection 3562, an incident occurred that toppled a mobile trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this became huge news just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did I have to bring him home with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} Yuma's making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma's throwing a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from? Why do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should help out a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Duel {\i1}Karaage{\i0}!\N ["Duel Fried Chicken strips"]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel {\i1}Yakiniku{\i0}\N ["Duel Grilled Fish (Or Meat)"]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel-{\i1}jiru{\i0}!\N ["Soup with Dueling in it"]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Duel {\i1}Nikujaga{\i0}!\N ["Duel Meat-Potato"]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say {\i1}itadakimasu{\i0} first!\N [Expression of gratitude]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's bad manners when we're in front of a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Itadakimasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, this {\i1}nikujaga{\i0} is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it! Eat your fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't gonna eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel the need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe {\i1}you{\i0} should hold back some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why're you singling me out?\N - Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I haven't gotten to eat much.\N - Liar! You ate a ton of meat already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you eat with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask for seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. If you find the boy, notify me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to lay your hands on him, or you'll end up like that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder where that kid came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no way of contacting Kaito, and I don't know where the guy's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito? If you meet him, you may end up Dueling against him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what happens happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of things I want to ask him... Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that he knows something about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, tomorrow I'll take him-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Where the heck did Haruto run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be another incident like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Was like an explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the deal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Haruto's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he might still be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for Kaito, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I promise I'll bring you back to Kaito's place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a response at Block B-12.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The change in atmosphere after a dimensional overspill ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy just used his power. He's in high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really trying to go meet Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, more than likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay boy, your evening stroll ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for me to feel. Why are you with Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... He kinda... spent the night with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get a damn thing you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, boy. We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do with Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto doesn't look like he wants to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a persistent brat! He's just going back to Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, let's go back to Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There's a large rise in the dimensional distribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The controls...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche! Are you safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to Kaito, I'm definitely gonna take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's with those middle school brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Find them at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kaito on the other side of that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaito's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone... Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean he's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were looking for Kaito... for your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really small...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small and sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my brother isn't around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this light different from the other times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this light be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We should be fine after coming this far. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto, I will protect you at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's called caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's got a magical power that makes you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eat it, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delicious...! It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? But what about you, Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fine so long as you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto... I'll stay with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, let's go back to Heartland, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BROTHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's searching for something called caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we need caramel for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto likely came here so Kaito could give him caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kaito could?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Yuma! At this rate, Haruto's power will swallow up everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, why do you want caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any caramel on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! This is what you're after, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted Kaito to give this to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...meet with Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, you aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is... always tired because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I wanted to give my brother caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to eat the caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Haruto's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two were running away from something and were cornered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he saw Haruto was nervous and sad, Kaito gave it to him to give him courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than likely, he wanted to do the same for his brother Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys just won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you take Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want some of this, come and-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will grant Haruto-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Haruto-{\i1}sama{\i0} wanted to see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to destroy the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to produce more screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...! Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... Just who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy we handed Haruto over hasn't returned yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a white stone inside the rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear his voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I promised Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I would definitely reunite you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Haruto's Gone! A New Enemy, Tron"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito sure is worried about Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I think about it, that's just how you treat a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how sibling relationships work?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I sure want a sibling!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have one right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
